fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.connector

Interface IConnector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttachable, Iterable<ISource>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IPlatformConnector

    @PluginService
public interface IConnector
extends IAttachable, Iterable<ISource>
    Connector to a data provider for ViewShell.

    Connectors can be used directly in for-each constructs, to iterate over data sources.

    Thread safety: implementations are required to be safe for concurrent access.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
